Attributes used to style the Action Bar.

Includes the following attributes:

AttributeDescription
com.actionbarsherlock:background Specifies a background drawable for the action bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:backgroundSplit Specifies a background drawable for the bottom component of a split action bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:backgroundStacked Specifies a background drawable for a second stacked row of the action bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:customNavigationLayout Specifies a layout for custom navigation.
com.actionbarsherlock:displayOptions Options affecting how the action bar is displayed.
com.actionbarsherlock:divider Specifies the drawable used for item dividers.
com.actionbarsherlock:height Specifies a fixed height.
com.actionbarsherlock:homeLayout Specifies a layout to use for the "home" section of the action bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:icon Specifies the drawable used for the application icon.
com.actionbarsherlock:indeterminateProgressStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an indeterminate progress spinner.
com.actionbarsherlock:itemPadding Specifies padding that should be applied to the left and right sides of system-provided items in the bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:logo Specifies the drawable used for the application logo.
com.actionbarsherlock:navigationMode The type of navigation to use.
com.actionbarsherlock:progressBarPadding Specifies the horizontal padding on either end for an embedded progress bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:progressBarStyle Specifies a style resource to use for an embedded progress bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:subtitle Specifies subtitle text used for navigationMode="normal"
com.actionbarsherlock:subtitleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for subtitle text.
com.actionbarsherlock:title Specifies title text used for navigationMode="normal"
com.actionbarsherlock:titleTextStyle Specifies a style to use for title text.

SherlockTheme

public static final int[] SherlockTheme
Attributes that can be used with a SherlockTheme.

Includes the following attributes:

AttributeDescription
com.actionbarsherlock:absForceOverflow Specified if we are forcing an action item overflow menu.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarDivider Custom divider drawable to use for elements in the action bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarItemBackground Custom item state list drawable background for action bar items.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarSize Size of the Action Bar, including the contextual bar used to present Action Modes.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarSplitStyle Reference to a style for the split Action Bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarStyle Reference to a style for the Action Bar
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarTabBarStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarTabStyle Default style for tabs within an action bar
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarTabTextStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:actionBarWidgetTheme Reference to a theme that should be used to inflate widgets and layouts destined for the action bar.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionButtonStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:actionDropDownStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:actionMenuTextAppearance TextAppearance style that will be applied to text that appears within action menu items.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionMenuTextColor Color for text that appears within action menu items.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionModeBackground Background drawable to use for action mode UI
com.actionbarsherlock:actionModeCloseButtonStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:actionModeCloseDrawable Drawable to use for the close action mode button
com.actionbarsherlock:actionModePopupWindowStyle PopupWindow style to use for action modes when showing as a window overlay.
com.actionbarsherlock:actionModeShareDrawable Drawable to use for the Share action button in WebView selection action modes
com.actionbarsherlock:actionModeSplitBackground Background drawable to use for action mode UI in the lower split bar
com.actionbarsherlock:actionModeStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:actionOverflowButtonStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:actionSpinnerItemStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:activatedBackgroundIndicator Drawable used as a background for activated items.
com.actionbarsherlock:activityChooserViewStyle Default ActivityChooserView style.
com.actionbarsherlock:android_windowIsFloating
com.actionbarsherlock:buttonStyleSmall Small Button style.
com.actionbarsherlock:dividerVertical Drawable to use for generic vertical dividers.
com.actionbarsherlock:dropDownListViewStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:dropdownListPreferredItemHeight
com.actionbarsherlock:homeAsUpIndicator
com.actionbarsherlock:listPopupWindowStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:listPreferredItemHeightSmall A smaller, sleeker list item height.
com.actionbarsherlock:listPreferredItemPaddingLeft The preferred padding along the left edge of list items.
com.actionbarsherlock:listPreferredItemPaddingRight The preferred padding along the right edge of list items.
com.actionbarsherlock:popupMenuStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:spinnerDropDownItemStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:spinnerItemStyle
com.actionbarsherlock:textAppearanceLargePopupMenu Text color, typeface, size, and style for the text inside of a popup menu.
com.actionbarsherlock:textAppearanceListItemSmall The preferred TextAppearance for the primary text of small list items.
com.actionbarsherlock:textAppearanceSmall Text color, typeface, size, and style for "small" text.
com.actionbarsherlock:textAppearanceSmallPopupMenu Text color, typeface, size, and style for small text inside of a popup menu.
com.actionbarsherlock:textColorPrimary
com.actionbarsherlock:textColorPrimaryDisableOnly
com.actionbarsherlock:textColorPrimaryInverse
com.actionbarsherlock:windowActionBar
com.actionbarsherlock:windowActionBarOverlay
com.actionbarsherlock:windowActionModeOverlay
com.actionbarsherlock:windowContentOverlay This Drawable is overlaid over the foreground of the Window's content area, usually to place a shadow below the title.
com.actionbarsherlock:windowMinWidthMajor
com.actionbarsherlock:windowMinWidthMinor
com.actionbarsherlock:windowNoTitle
com.actionbarsherlock:windowSplitActionBar
